verses.verse: Praise <S%H1984><s%> ye the LORD. <S%H3050><s%> Praise <S%H1984><s%> <S%H853><s%> the LORD, <S%H3068><s%> O my soul. <S%H5315><s%>
While I live <S%H2416><s%> will I praise <S%H1984><s%> the LORD: <S%H3068><s%> I will sing praises <S%H2167><s%> unto my God <S%H430><s%> while I have any being. <S%H5750><s%>
Put not <S%H408><s%> your trust <S%H982><s%> in princes, <S%H5081><s%> nor in the son <S%H1121><s%> of man, <S%H120><s%> in whom there is no <S%H7945><s%> <S%H369><s%> help. <S%H8668><s%>
His breath <S%H7307><s%> goeth forth, <S%H3318><s%> he returneth <S%H7725><s%> to his earth; <S%H127><s%> in that very <S%H1931><s%> day <S%H3117><s%> his thoughts <S%H6250><s%> perish. <S%H6><s%>

Happy <S%H835><s%> is he that hath the God <S%H7945><s%> <S%H410><s%> of Jacob <S%H3290><s%> for his help, <S%H5828><s%> whose hope <S%H7664><s%> is in <S%H5921><s%> the LORD <S%H3068><s%> his God: <S%H430><s%>

Which made <S%H6213><s%> heaven, <S%H8064><s%> and earth, <S%H776><s%> <S%H853><s%> the sea, <S%H3220><s%> and all <S%H3605><s%> that <S%H834><s%> therein is: which keepeth <S%H8104><s%> truth <S%H571><s%> forever: <S%H5769><s%>

Which executeth <S%H6213><s%> judgment <S%H4941><s%> for the oppressed: <S%H6231><s%> which giveth <S%H5414><s%> food <S%H3899><s%> to the hungry. <S%H7457><s%> The LORD <S%H3068><s%> looseth <S%H5425><s%> the prisoners: <S%H631><s%>

The LORD <S%H3068><s%> openeth <S%H6491><s%> the eyes of the blind: <S%H5787><s%> the LORD <S%H3068><s%> raiseth <S%H2210><s%> them that are bowed down: <S%H3721><s%> the LORD <S%H3068><s%> loveth <S%H157><s%> the righteous: <S%H6662><s%>

The LORD <S%H3068><s%> preserveth <S%H8104><s%> <S%H853><s%> the strangers; <S%H1616><s%> he relieveth <S%H5749><s%> the fatherless <S%H3490><s%> and widow: <S%H490><s%> but the way <S%H1870><s%> of the wicked <S%H7563><s%> he turneth upside down. <S%H5791><s%>

The LORD <S%H3068><s%> shall reign <S%H4427><s%> forever, <S%H5769><s%> even thy God, <S%H430><s%> O Zion, <S%H6726><s%> unto all generations. <S%H1755><s%> <S%H1755><s%> Praise <S%H1984><s%> ye the LORD. <S%H3050><s%>
